----------------------------------------
 1. USER REGISTRATION
----------------------------------------

‚ùå 1.1 Missing required fields

curl -i -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/users \
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
-d '{
  "firstName": "Alice"
}'

Expected:
HTTP/1.1 400 Bad Request  
{"error":"Missing fields: lastName, username, password"}


‚úÖ 1.2 Successful registration

curl -i -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/users \
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
-d '{
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Test",
  "username": "alice123",
  "password": "securepass"
}'

Expected:
HTTP/1.1 201 Created  
Location: /api/users/1

‚ùå 1.3 Duplicate username

curl -i -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/users \
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
-d '{
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Test2",
  "username": "alice123",
  "password": "newpass"
}'

Expected:
HTTP/1.1 400 Bad Request  
{"error":"Username already exists."}

‚ùå 1.4 Missing content in required fields in registration

curl -i -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/users \
-H "Content-Type: application/json" \
-d '{
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "",
  "username": "alice1234",
  "password": "securepass"
}'

Expected:
HTTP/1.1 400 Bad Request  
{"error":"Missing fields: lastName"}

